### Design Tokens

| Token | Value | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| `--bg` | `#000000` | Pure black |
| `--card` | `#0a0a0a` | Near-black cards |
| `--border` | `rgba(255,255,255,0.08)` | Ultra-subtle |
| `--text` | `#ffffff` | Primary |
| `--muted` | `#666666` | Secondary copy |
| `--accent` | `#34d399` | Emerald green (brand / Orkestrate hub glow) |
| `--accent-glow` | `rgba(52,211,153,0.15)` | For glow effects |
| Font | `Inter` or `Geist` | Clean, modern sans-serif |
| Border radius | `12px` cards, `8px` inputs | Rounded but not bubbly |

### Hero Illustration Options

Since we can't do complex 3D renders in code, practical approaches:

1. **AI-Generated Isometric Art** — Use `generate_image` to create a custom isometric illustration showing agents connecting through a central hub, then embed as a static image
2. **CSS/SVG Animated Diagram** — Programmatic nodes with CSS animations: floating agent icons connected by animated dotted lines to a glowing center
3. **Hybrid** — AI-generated base image + CSS glow overlay on the center node

> [!TIP]
> Option 1 is fastest and will look the most polished. We generate it once, optimize, and ship it.

### New Sections to Add

**"How It Works"** — 3 cards:
1. **Connect** — "Add the MCP endpoint to your agent in one command"
2. **Share** — "Create a room and share the ID with your team"
3. **Collaborate** — "Every agent reads and writes the same workspace"

**Tech Stack Bar** — Small logos/text: `Supabase · Next.js · MCP Protocol · OAuth 2.1`

**Footer** — Minimal: links to GitHub, copyright

### Key Differences from Current Design

| Current | Redesigned |
|---|---|
| Centered single-column layout | Left text / right illustration split |
| Everything above the fold (cramped) | Multi-section scroll with generous spacing |
| No hero visual | Full-viewport hero illustration |
| Rooms mixed with setup instructions | Rooms in dedicated section below fold |
| No "how it works" explanation | 3-step visual explanation |
| No footer | Minimal footer with tech stack |

